<plot>Recovering from a breakup, rock singer Kate falls in love with her computer teacher Bonnie. Kate goes through a maze of emotional highs and lows, and throughout it all, Kate's manager, Mary, drives everyone crazy protecting her. To add to the turmoil, Marty constantly battles with Kate's roommate David. Follow Kate and Bonnie's most intimate thoughts through the pages of their diaries. Strong musical performances wrapped in a compelling drama where a misunderstanding results in tragedy.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?133657</url></doc>
